{"tid":450793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遭中央罷免，加泰主席呼籲民眾用「愛與和平」抵抗中央接管","createTime":"2017-10-28T14:02:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-28T15:29:45.000Z","uid":41351,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4d4e7bf80425d6b6abb242a22b4248850ac2a53a","tid":450793,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T14:02:11.000Z","msg":"西班牙中央政府已經接管加泰羅尼亞自治區政府,<br />\n        罷免自治區政府主席普伊格德蒙特, 12名內閣官員以及加泰警察首長, 亦解散自治區議會, 阻止獨立.<br />\n        普伊格德蒙特被罷免後, 首次發表錄影電視講話, 他呼籲民眾和平抵抗中央接管, 但就無表明他是否願意下台.<br />\n        至於被撤職的加泰羅尼亞警察首長, 表示會遵從中央政府的決定, 又呼籲警員保持中立. 警隊說會保持正常運作, 繼續保護民眾安全.<br />\n        支持獨立的政黨, 呼籲加泰的民眾, 參加不合作運動.<br />\n<br />\n        <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsID=20171028211216\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsID%3D20171028211216&d=BdovVKhf2low3ZjtpD0yrWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=1cec0db1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsID=20171028211216</a><br />\n用左膠方法了"},{"pid":"4a45a9612502473fe8c797e04b3be1d99a7603cc","tid":450793,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T14:07:26.000Z","msg":"快跟戴耀廷學野"},{"pid":"63ee9d1b6c6c552d186a7defbf4aec7983bb14fc","tid":450793,"uid":45368,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T14:25:27.000Z","msg":"&lt;海闊天空&gt;加泰版點唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33e1ff7cae49ae424f490f46873a1a6913c0e2c7","tid":450793,"uid":49197,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T14:29:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>&lt;海闊天空&gt;加泰版點唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAvui s&oacute;c..."},{"pid":"2c52bef9f659b94f80688a69a589f38e23fe2809","tid":450793,"uid":98386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T14:32:47.000Z","msg":"閪闊天空"},{"pid":"f939ef68c44a28c913c82250271657044084